@page "/registry"

<div class="registry-page">
    <h1 class="registry-title">Registry</h1>
    <p class="registry-subtitle">Your presence is truly the greatest gift.<br />But if you'd like to give something more, we'd be so grateful.</p>

    <div class="registry-card">
        <div class="registry-logo-wrap">
            <img src="images/amazon.jpg" alt="Amazon" class="registry-logo" />
        </div>
        <p class="registry-description">
            We've put together a wish list of things we love on Amazon.
            From home essentials to a few fun extras — there's something for every budget.
        </p>
        <a class="registry-btn" href="https://www.amazon.com/" target="_blank">
            View Our Amazon Registry
        </a>
    </div>

    <p class="registry-note">
        Can't find something you love? A heartfelt card means the world to us too.
    </p>
</div>